snippet.title: Purpose: VERSUS (& VERSA) | Cinematic Trailer
snippet.description:
All links: https://flow.page/projectpurpose

After 2 - 3 months in the making, I am proud to present the cinematic trailer for Purpose: VERSUS (and it’s animated series counterpart - Purpose: VERSA), in which the story of Kaleb and Tobias is put into context for the first time.


PATREON: https://patreon.com/STEPHENDDUNGU


Which character do you prefer? Kaleb or Tobias? Let me know in the comments!

_________________________________________________
Voices:

Kaleb: Corey Holland.
https://twitter.com/CoreyHolland

https://twitter.com/keanudonut

District Officers: Lane H Rush
